abstract: Stocks climb to finish strongest week in almost three months.

headline.print_headline: Shares Wrap Up Best Week in 3 Months
headline.main: Wall St. Wraps Up Strong Week on a High Note

snippet: Bank shares were higher after the head of the Federal Reserve confirmed it would keep raising interest rates, provided the economy kept improving.
lead_paragraph: Bank shares were higher after the head of the Federal Reserve confirmed it would keep raising interest rates, provided the economy kept improving.
